Seminar

Burkitt’s lymphoma

Elizabeth M Molyneux, Rosemary Rochford, Beverly Griﬃn, Robert Newton, Graham Jackson, Geetha Menon, Christine J Harrison, Trijn Israels, Simon Bailey

Lancet 2012; 379: 1234–44
Published Online February 13, 2012 DOI:10.1016/S01406736(11)61177-X
